PrecisAuthorization for THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to enter into a number of insurance contracts with certain purveyors of insurance in order to provide its employees and their dependents with group life insurance, long-term disability, accidental death, travel, dental and group medical insurance plans, and to pay its portion of the premiums.
